name: Jedi Escape
Lore: 'Qui-Gon escaped with his friends from Tatooine, barely getting away from the clutches of Darth Maul.',
Text: 'If opponent just initiated a duel against one of your non-captive Jedi at a site, use 1 Force to cancel the duel and you may relocate any number of your characters there to an adjacent site.',
